text: Nathan Sheafor (born November 16, 1961) is an American former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the United States Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Fort Bragg, North Carolina Category:Sportspeople from North Carolina
